{"id": 993, "genre": 1001, "title": "你无法忍受哪些敷衍的服务？", "description": "“请问有什么可以帮您……您的申诉已提交，请等待我们的工作人员跟您联系”（题图来自：Zara Picken）", "record_count": 4240, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183948D7ytncaTSX0MRLHY.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-02T01:00:17Z", "options": [{"id": 102912, "content": "行，我过两天一定帮你看看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 370121}, {"id": 94722, "content": "Uber取消费", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75801}, {"id": 104197, "content": "我们只是服务人员", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700756}, {"id": 94726, "content": "半小时内一定回复您", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664754}, {"id": 94727, "content": "外卖马上就到，外卖已经到了下来拿一下，永远下楼第一时间见不到", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664754}, {"id": 94729, "content": "马上，马上？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 506150}, {"id": 94730, "content": "这事不归我们管。嘿嘿，我们调查调查。你替谁说话？爱哪告哪告去！", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262394}, {"id": 94731, "content": "没办法，系统就是这样规定的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 661976}, {"id": 94733, "content": "微信团队！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664769}, {"id": 94736, "content": "“亲，我帮你去XXXX～”", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651792}, {"id": 94996, "content": "菜马上就好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126700}, {"id": 94742, "content": "快递迟迟不到，问总是说已发货", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664786}, {"id": 94747, "content": "啊你要的是 粉啊，我做成饭了。您看，这做都做了，要不您将就一下？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 51431}, {"id": 94748, "content": "您的意见我们已记录，请耐心等待处理结果。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492960}, {"id": 95004, "content": "菜一会就上来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637289}, {"id": 94749, "content": "fuck", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659339}, {"id": 110623, "content": "“对不起，我错了”", "image": "img/option/option/20160825175332W4KYSFAEhVRklDZr.png", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 732145}, {"id": 94753, "content": "等一下........然后，然后没了！！！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664027}, {"id": 94758, "content": "为什么？没有钱啊？努力了还是没有钱？\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664851}, {"id": 94760, "content": "我去后台给你催催", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 552461}, {"id": 94761, "content": "银行，通信，航空公司的服务都无法忍受！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663178}, {"id": 112169, "content": "我要问一下上级", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741508}, {"id": 94762, "content": "“我的外卖已经一个小时了怎么还没送到?!”\n“不好意思，你的外卖刚送出去，请稍等。”\n——又一小时以后\n“你的外卖到了，下来拿下外卖。”\n???", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663413}, {"id": 95274, "content": "菜已经在锅里了，正给您催着呢～\n通线忙，请稍候再拨打～\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614327}, {"id": 95020, "content": "马上就去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 564197}, {"id": 95022, "content": "地铁安检", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144646}, {"id": 94767, "content": "你的催单已提交！商家会尽快回复你的催单(¯Д¯)ノ", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 413074}, {"id": 94768, "content": "最讨厌明明没到却说：马上到！马上到！有时还没出门却说在路上在路上了", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 606147}, {"id": 94769, "content": "当前人工坐席忙，请挂机。滴滴滴滴滴滴滴滴滴~~~~~~???", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664941}, {"id": 95281, "content": "“来碗牛肉面，多肉多汤少辣不要香菜！”“好嘞，一碗牛肉面！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607915}, {"id": 94771, "content": "屈臣士结帐：我们最近搞优惠，买满换购……你看你还需要啥不……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307916}, {"id": 95028, "content": "为人民服务", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665588}, {"id": 94775, "content": "你点的菜马上就来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660917}, {"id": 106808, "content": "“马上就好了，再等等”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711860}, {"id": 94786, "content": "每天叫uber， 50%以上都是完全不认识路的外地司机 ，很多连普通话都说不清楚，滴滴也是同样情况，深恶痛绝！", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664963}, {"id": 95043, "content": "“顾客的声音始终是我们最为重视的，我们会将您的意见传递至公司相关负责团队，希望他们可以及时聆听顾客的需求并积极计划改进”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289728}, {"id": 94788, "content": "稍等一下我问一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656148}, {"id": 94792, "content": "不行，必须要本人来", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664584}, {"id": 95048, "content": "打人工服务总说非常抱歉", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233837}, {"id": 94793, "content": "“您的菜我去催一催”", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 661495}, {"id": 94799, "content": "规定就是这样，我也没办法。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 662149}, {"id": 95055, "content": "甜品面包店，“请问这款里有什么（食材）？”“？？？没吃过”…那你推销个毛线???", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665662}, {"id": 95311, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648471}, {"id": 94800, "content": "快递显示签收，然而并没有送到", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630546}, {"id": 95057, "content": "网络繁忙", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665627}, {"id": 94803, "content": "先生，您做大活儿还是小活儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 625365}, {"id": 94804, "content": "这个不是我们负责的，请找别的部门", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657209}, {"id": 94805, "content": "淘宝客服 在的，亲～", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647178}, {"id": 94806, "content": "新浪客服", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 650905}, {"id": 94808, "content": "“翻水鱼”自助餐吃到后面让老板加鱼?，永远是“马上就来”……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654332}]}